WEBVTT

00:00:18.706 --> 00:00:25.087 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
When he was young, David loved God.
He prayed to him and sang him songs.

00:00:25.087 --> 00:00:31.677 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
His God looked down, heard him sing;
Then He chose him to be king.

00:00:31.677 --> 00:00:43.355 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
He faced a bear and a lion with its claws.
He was not scared because

00:00:44.064 --> 00:00:56.869 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
David—David—trusted in his God.
Jehovah saved him and helped him all along.

00:00:56.869 --> 00:01:09.715 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
I will pray ev’ry day just like David did.
Iʼll remember Jehovah and trust in Him.

00:01:23.938 --> 00:01:30.444 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
